    Draw the map focused on one project

    draw_map_focus_one_project(
  projects_data_sf,
  id_project,
  cantons_sf = NULL,
  zoom_level = 8
)

    Arguments

    projects_data_sf

    A sf data.frame containing coordinates of project main organisation and project `short_title`.

    id_project

    Character. Id of the project.

    cantons_sf

    Sf data. Cantons geometry. Mainly used for examples and unit testing purpose.

    zoom_level

    An integer. The zoom level for the map. Defines default zoom level.

    Value

    A leaflet object.

    Examples

    data("toy_projects_data_sf")
data("toy_cantons_sf")

draw_map_focus_one_project(
  projects_data_sf = toy_projects_data_sf,
  id_project = "1+1=3  PGV03.038", 
  cantons_sf = toy_cantons_sf
)
